%% ModelMesh Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.25/modelmesh.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Controller
    participant MMApi as ModelMesh gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant MMCore as ModelMesh Core<br/>LRU Cache & Router
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (configurable)
    participant RemoteMM as Remote ModelMesh Pod<br/>8080/TCP Thrift/gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime Container<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>plaintext gRPC

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>MMApi: gRPC Inference RPC<br/>mm-model-id header<br/>TLS (optional)
    MMApi->>MMCore: Route by model ID
    MMCore->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>gRPC/TLS, client creds

    alt Model loaded locally
        MMCore->>Runtime: Forward inference<br/>gRPC (plaintext, localhost)
        Runtime-->>MMCore: Prediction result
    else Model on remote pod
        MMCore->>RemoteMM: Forward via Litelinks<br/>Thrift/gRPC, TLS (when configured)
        RemoteMM->>Runtime: Forward inference<br/>gRPC (plaintext, localhost)
        Runtime-->>RemoteMM: Prediction result
        RemoteMM-->>MMCore: Response
    end

    MMCore-->>MMApi: Inference result
    MMApi-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>TLS (optional)

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Registration

    Client->>MMApi: registerModel RPC<br/>gRPC/TLS (optional)
    MMApi->>MMCore: Register model
    MMCore->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC/TLS, client creds
    etcd-->>MMCore: Confirmation

    alt loadNow=true
        MMCore->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC (plaintext, localhost)
        Runtime-->>MMCore: Model loaded
    end

    MMCore-->>MMApi: Registration result
    MMApi-->>Client: ModelStatusInfo

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Cache Eviction & Rebalancing

    MMCore->>MMCore: LRU eviction triggered
    MMCore->>Runtime: unloadModel RPC<br/>gRPC (plaintext, localhost)
    Runtime-->>MMCore: Model unloaded
    MMCore->>etcd: Update model placement<br/>gRPC/TLS, client creds
    MMCore->>RemoteMM: Trigger load on target pod<br/>Litelinks
    RemoteMM->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC (plaintext, localhost)
    Runtime-->>RemoteMM: Model loaded
